## Verification

This report is signed with the Jelleo Ed25519 platform key. To verify:

```
audit-pipeline sign verify {{REPORT_FILENAME}} {{REPORT_FILENAME}}.sig \
    --pubkey jelleo.ed25519.pub
```

The published Jelleo public key is mirrored in:

- The platform repo: `https://github.com/Copenhagen0x/audit-pipeline-cli/blob/main/keys/jelleo.ed25519.pub`
- The methodology page: [jelleo.com/methodology.html#attestation](https://jelleo.com/methodology.html#attestation)

A valid signature confirms (a) the report bytes have not been altered since signing, and (b) the cycle ran in a Jelleo workspace whose private key matches the published public key.

