## Methodology

The audit methodology, hypothesis library schema, severity rubric, lifecycle state machine, and propagation engine are documented at:

**[jelleo.com/methodology.html](https://jelleo.com/methodology.html)**

For a deeper walkthrough of the four-pillar architecture and how findings move from `new` → `verified`, see methodology §06 (lifecycle) and §07 (attestation).

