## Disclosure policy

Findings of severity Critical or High are disclosed to the maintainer before public release. Standard responsible-disclosure window: **30 days from `confirmed` → public**, extensible by mutual agreement when a fix is in flight. See [jelleo.com/security.html](https://jelleo.com/security.html) for the full policy.

